    "body": "I would go with a subset of JavaScript's syntax.\r\n\r\n1) Exporting a symbol that is being defined.\r\n```\r\nexport contract Foo { }\r\n```\r\n\r\n2) Exporting previously defined or imported symbols.\r\n```\r\nexport { Bar, Qux };\r\n```\r\n\r\nSymbols can be contracts, interfaces, or libraries.",
