    "body": "Imports should not be re exported by default. One of the motivations for this feature is that tools will generate compilation artifacts for all of the \"exported\" contracts contained in the solc output. If importing contracts from a smart contract library this can result in a lot of compilation artifacts the user doesn't care about, because everything that was imported will now be exported.",
